-(NSString *)content{
    return @"<p><strong>出行准备</strong><br />\n<strong>关于车票</strong></p>\n<p>在上海出行，建议选择地铁3日票</p>\n<p>此次安排的行程是4天，3日票是45元，1日票是18元，当然是3日票合算；<br />\n此次安排的行程基本要做地铁，大概算 下，还是买3日票比单程票合算；<br />\n3日票真的很方便，72小时内无限次乘坐地铁，而且是刷卡进出，省去每次乘地铁买票的时间！！大力推荐那些出行 坐地铁较多的驴友~~~<br />\n<strong>关于住宿</strong><br />\n此次行程以7天酒店为例，上海7天连锁酒店（西藏南路地铁站店）为什么选这家呢？交通真的是太方便了，西藏南路地铁站1号出口出来立马能看到！！闹中取静！！！出门4号和8号地铁，旁边两个便利店，十分方便，而且西藏南路地铁站人不多，出行真的清静很多！！</p>\n<p>如果选择其他酒店，建议选择市中心靠近地铁站的酒店。</p>\n<p><strong>行程安排</strong><br />\n第一天<br />\n到上海，外白渡桥，甜爱路，徐家汇天主教堂，港汇恒隆广场（Godiva，板长寿司，Laduree马卡龙，鼎泰丰）<br />\n第二天<br />\n鲜得来排骨年糕(云南南路店)，朱家角（三阳小楼），七宝古镇，Disney旗舰店，正大广场（Cold Stone），耳光馄饨，长脚汤面<br />\n第三天<br />\n上海影视乐园，香港广场，连卡佛，环球金融中心，IFC<br />\n第四天<br />\nM&amp;M&#8217;S，吴江路</p>\n<p><strong>第一天</strong></p>\n<p>外白渡桥-甜爱路-港汇恒隆广场</p>\n<p>中午没在动车上就餐，一下车第一件事当然是去吃个午餐，虹桥动车站有好多吃的，如味千拉面，康师傅牛肉面，东方既白，真功夫，赛百味等等。<br />\n就餐完毕，去旁边地铁服务站买了三日游地铁票，72小时内无限次乘坐地铁，而且是刷卡进出，省去每次乘地铁买票的时间！！！</p>\n<p>虹桥火车站<br />\n上海虹桥到7天西藏南路店<br />\n趁乘坐10号地铁（新江湾城方向）13站，老西门换乘8号线（沈杜公路方向），西藏南路站下车，1号出口，出口后就能看到。。。！！！绝对方便。。。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-118\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/1-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>酒店放置好行李，开始上海之旅了啦~~~O(∩_∩)O~~<br />\n第一站：外白渡桥<br />\n7天西藏南路店到外白渡桥<br />\n乘坐8号线，在老西门站换乘10号线，南京东路站下车，6号出口，出口后导航一下，步行10分钟左右就能看到了。。。！</p>\n<p>地铁站到外白渡桥拍得建筑</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/3.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-120\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/3-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/4.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-121\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/4-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a>  <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-119\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/2-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"201\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/13.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-117\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/13-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/12.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-116\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/12-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/11.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-115\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/11-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/10.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-114\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/10-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/8.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-112\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/8-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/9.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-113\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/9-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\n<p>第二站：甜爱路<br />\n外白渡桥到甜爱路：步行到海宁路吴淞路公交站，导航一下吧，乘坐854或939，甜爱路四川北路站下车。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-126\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/1-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"201\" height=\"300\" /></a>  <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-128\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/3-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/4.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-129\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/4-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"201\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\n第三站：天主教堂<br />\n甜爱路到徐家汇教堂，由于买了地铁3日票，果断选择找地铁站，步行到虹口足球场站，乘坐8号线（沈杜公路），在陆家浜路站换乘9号线（松江南站），徐家汇下车，3号出口</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/11.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-130\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/11-169x300.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"169\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/21.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-131\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/21-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\n第四站：港汇恒隆广场<br />\n徐家汇天主教堂到港汇恒隆广场还算近，导航步行过去。。。<br />\n去港汇目的就是为了吃，板长寿司，Laduree，Godiva，鼎泰丰，吃吃吃！！！！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/12.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-133\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/12-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\n港汇恒隆广场<br />\n炸虾饼</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/22.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-134\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/22-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a><br />\n港汇恒隆广场<br />\n鹅肝寿司，22元/个，很好食，鹅肝入口即化的赶脚。。。！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/32.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-135\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/32-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/41.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-136\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/41-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a></p>\n<p>港汇恒隆广场<br />\n熔岩蛋糕很不好吃，里面整个空心的，建议不要点了，20元/个</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/5.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-137\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/5-226x300.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"226\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/6.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-138\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/6-226x300.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"226\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/7.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-139\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/7-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\n米其林一星餐厅——鼎泰丰，绝对赞，收10%的服务费。。。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/8.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-140\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/8-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/9.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-141\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/9-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/10.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-142\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/10-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\nLaduree，法国正宗马卡龙</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/111.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-143\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/111-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/13.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-145\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/13-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/121.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-144\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/121-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\nGodiva——冰淇淋中的爱马仕</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/14.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-146\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/14-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/15.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-147\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/15-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\n第二天</p>\n<p>朱家角-七宝老街-Disney旗舰店-正大广场-肇周路<br />\n今天行程要去朱家角和七宝古镇逛逛，推荐鲜得来排骨年糕10元/份</p>\n<p>酒店出发到鲜得来：乘坐8号线（市光路方向），在大世界站下车，1号出口，往云南路方向走</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/16.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-148\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/16-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\n鲜得来排骨年糕(云南南路店)<br />\n吃饱了，出发朱家角古镇，步行到普安路延安东路站，乘坐沪朱高速快线，朱家角汽车站下车。。。大概2小时左右就能到达古镇。。。！！！票价：12元/人</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/51.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-149\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/51-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/61.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-150\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/61-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/71.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-151\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/71-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/81.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-152\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/81-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/91.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-153\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/91-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/101.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-154\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/101-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/112.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-155\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/112-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/23.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-156\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/23-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"201\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/33.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-157\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/33-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/42.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-158\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/42-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a></p>\n<p>午餐在三阳小楼就餐，坐在湖边吃饭，感觉美滋滋的。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/122.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-159\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/122-169x300.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"169\" height=\"300\" /></a><br />\n游完朱家角古镇，出发七宝古镇。。。！<br />\n在朱家角汽车站坐松朱专线，票价：5元/人，塘桥站下车，在洞泾地铁站乘9号地铁，七宝站下车，1出口</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/34.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-160\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/34-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/43.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-161\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/43-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/52.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-162\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/52-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/62.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-163\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/62-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/72.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-164\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/72-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/82.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-165\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/82-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/17.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-166\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/17-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/24.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-167\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/24-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"201\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>七宝老街到Disney旗舰店，乘坐9号线，世纪公园站换乘2号线，陆家嘴站下车</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/25.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-169\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/25-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a>  <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/44.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-171\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/44-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>顺道到旁边的小杨生煎吃个生煎包。。。小杨生煎我的爱啊。。。！双拼（猪肉+虾）13元/份</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/19.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-172\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/19-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a><br />\n小杨生煎(东方明珠店)<br />\n再到对面的正大广场逛逛，买个我最爱吃的冰淇淋Cold Stone</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/26.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-173\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/26-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/36.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-174\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/36-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a></p>\n<p>吃完冰淇淋然后又去肇周路找美食，长脚汤面和耳光馄饨。。。<br />\n长脚汤面加肉加菜：30元<br />\n耳光馄饨：猪排加馄饨21元</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/110.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-175\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/110-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/27.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-176\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/27-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>第三天</strong></p>\n<p>上海车墩影视乐园-香港广场-连卡佛-环球金融中心-IFC<br />\n今天要去上海影视乐园，建议在上海南站坐火车再公交，可以省时；此次行程还是以地铁莲花站下车，再转坐莲石线，车墩站下车为线路</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/113.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-177\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/113-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/28.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-178\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/28-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/37.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-179\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/37-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/45.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-180\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/45-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/53.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-181\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/53-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/63.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-182\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/63-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/73.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-183\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/73-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/83.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-184\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/83-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"8\" width=\"201\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/92.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-185\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/92-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"9\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/102.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-186\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/102-300x201.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"300\" height=\"201\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/114.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-187\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/114-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a><br />\n今天还有个目的地是环球金融中心观光，原本94,97,100层观光门票要180，可以在淘宝订了一个团队票是110，但是需要在指定时间，跟团进去，游完影视乐园还早，就觉得先去吃个午饭再喝个下午茶，然后前往环球金融中心观光<br />\n填饱肚子，就去下午茶，选择连卡佛里的Angelina，法国百年老店。。。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/115.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-188\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/115-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/29.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-189\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/29-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/38.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-190\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/38-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>第四天</strong></p>\n<p>M&amp;M&#8217;S-吴江路<br />\n今天要返程，简单的逛逛，选择M&amp;M&#8217;S和吴江路</p>\n<p>M&amp;M&#8217;S的彩虹长城太吸引眼球了。。。！！！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/116.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-191\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/116-300x104.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"300\" height=\"104\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/210.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-192\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/210-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a></p>\n<p>上海传说中的红宝石奶油小方！！</p>\n<p>在吴江路吃了中饭，就要离开上海这个繁华的城市了。。。！！</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/46.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-194\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/46-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/39.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-193\" src=\"http://www.kitty-travel.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/39-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n";
}

- (NSArray *)all_article_images{
    
    
    
    if (!_all_article_images) {
        
        NSData  * data      = [self.content dataUsingEncoding:NSUTF8StringEncoding];
        
        TFHpple * doc       = [[TFHpple alloc] initWithHTMLData:data];
        NSArray * elements  = [doc searchWithXPathQuery:@"//img"];
        NSMutableArray *imageUrls = [[NSMutableArray alloc] initWithCapacity:elements.count];

        [elements enumerateObjectsUsingBlock:^( TFHppleElement * element, NSUInteger idx, BOOL * _Nonnull stop) {
            NSDictionary *dic = element.attributes;

            [imageUrls addObject:dic[@"src"]];
        }];
        
        
        _all_article_images = imageUrls;
    }
    
    return _all_article_images;
}

